<h2>Sore tongue, Swollen lips and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms sore tongue, swollen lips and white patches on tongue including Allergic reaction, Thrush (infants and children), and Medication reaction or side-effect.</p>
<p>There  are 7 conditions  associated with sore tongue, swollen lips and white patches on tongue. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
